# agent-os Platform Reference

This document describes how the agent-os platform you are running on works **right now**. It is regenerated automatically each time the platform is updated (see `platform-changelog.md` for update history).

If this doc contradicts older docs in your company — runbooks, architecture notes, prior knowledge files — **trust this one**. Older docs are snapshots from an earlier version of the platform and may describe workflows that no longer exist.

